                <note rend="inline" type="source">71.1.21/507 Supp’l: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-10-30T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 30, 1919, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Kindly advise effect produced by Department’s October 13, 10 p.m. and October 14,
                    8 p.m. and indicate what action you think Colombia is likely to take with
                    respect to new proposed subsoil agreement.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
